"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"To give the measure of this omission, it is enough to think just of the educational system. Education is never taken account of as such at a time when it plays a determining role in the production of goods and services as in the production of the producers themselves. From this sort of original sin, inscribed in the Walrasian myth (1) of \\\"pure theory\\\", flow all of the deficiencies and faults of the discipline of economics and the fatal obstinacy with which it attaches itself to the arbitrary opposition which it induces, through its mere existence, between a properly economic logic, based on competition and efficiency, and social logic, which is subject to the rule of fairness.\",\"timestamp\":1638954456,\"title\":\" give the measure of this omission\"},\"digest\":\"ZF-II7WtU4m3xsdOLc3lz8R5vUhWhvGLRugyfu-MH8U\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8904a12B0a626C60b54f9776b3D171DFE05A098D\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"wL5Qrl-RnKMrgfM6OQqlcQP8fnkrdCBuElQKtNziEwY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"bYkCiZZZ_09YzyCotLD0Rt2tWpLiwv6RSO5kt77xVYg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"jX87JTDXEnEJrVjvqQ21By16DAIj7yXbyMOuaZ3otlgcXsUDPQO8EJQnHD77lzDzkzv-d7d8JGD9hKF3MLljSQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x34733a6e41f7a93216e66d71aead2e475eea11b3b55037a65587de0b56ac3ca427653f66eab12a51cfbed63e0b63dd10cada45ef6f08d1de15c6bcdd4fe440ad1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"wL5Qrl-RnKMrgfM6OQqlcQP8fnkrdCBuElQKtNziEwY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"bYkCiZZZ_09YzyCotLD0Rt2tWpLiwv6RSO5kt77xVYg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ZF-II7WtU4m3xsdOLc3lz8R5vUhWhvGLRugyfu-MH8U\"}"